Field.Name: DeviceDTM
Field.Description: A Device DTM contains the application software for a 'normal' field device, e.g. a pressure transmitter or, a valve or a drive.

Field.Name: CommunicationDTM
Field.Description: A Communication DTM is a special category of DTM containing the application software for specific communication hardware.

Field.Name: GatewayDTM
Field.Description: A Gateway DTM is a special category of DTM representing a device that connects different fieldbus segments.

Field.Name: CompositeDeviceDTM
Field.Description: A Composite DTM is a special category of DTM which is similar to a gateway DTM. A Composite DTM is the parent of a Module DTM and is intended to represent a header station of a modular device.

Field.Name: ModuleDTM
Field.Description: A Module DTM is a special kind of DTM which is similar to a device DTM. A Module DTM is a child of a Composite DTM and is intended to represent a single module of a modular device.

Field.Name: BlockTypeManager
Field.Description: A Block Type Manager (BTM) is a special category of DTM containing the application software for accessible objects inside a device such as function blocks and resource blocks. It is a child of a Device DTM.
